A yet-to-be-identified man has been electrocuted to death while trying to steal a transformer cable in Lagos island.
Although details of the incident are still stretchy, it was gathered that the thief met his waterloo after power was restored while he was trying to disconnect the cable.
According to report, the said cable was recently fixed after it was previously stolen by suspected hoodlums.
